44
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:16,660
Rest assured, I'm very good at biking.
She won't fall off it.

45
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:18,940
Do you think it's appropriate
to take Mengchen around here?

46
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:20,500
Absolutely, it's so romantic.

47
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,580
Play your romantic game alone.

48
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:23,340
Mengchen is going
to have Western cuisine with me.

49
00:02:23,340 --> 00:02:24,740
I can take her.

50
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:25,820
But she made plans with me.

51
00:02:25,980 --> 00:02:26,620
Count her out.

52
00:02:26,620 --> 00:02:27,660
Aren't you being too controlling?

53
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,460
Let go of...

54
00:02:30,940 --> 00:02:31,740
Mengchen.

55
00:02:31,900 --> 00:02:32,700
Brother,

56
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:37,060
I think the pastry I had just now
had sesame in it.

57
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:39,140
Did you get a rash?

58
00:02:39,220 --> 00:02:40,460
Mengchen, are you allergic to sesame?

59
00:02:40,780 --> 00:02:43,500
Mengchen, I really didn't know, I swear.

60
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,420
Qi Zeyu, do you have a death wish?

61
00:02:45,940 --> 00:02:46,900
I truly didn't know that.

62
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:48,660
What are you standing around for? Go!

63
00:02:48,660 --> 00:02:49,460
Go back to the clinic.

64
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:04,380
What are you doing?

65
00:03:04,540 --> 00:03:06,100
Bro, I'm a doctor.

66
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:08,100
I'll apply her ointment
and get rid of the rash.

67
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:12,820
Put it there. I'll help her.

68
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:15,740
But...

69
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,740
What are you waiting for? Get out.

70
00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:26,060
You're awake.

71
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:27,580
Feeling any better?

72
00:04:29,220 --> 00:04:31,060
- I'll do it myself.
- Don't move.

73
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:32,540
Just listen to me.

74
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:39,620
Since you get a rash,

75
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:40,700
