of anything too rich.

76
00:04:40,860 --> 00:04:42,460
The yellow croaker is off the menu today.

77
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:44,660
I'll make you some pork meatball soup
when we get home.

78
00:04:46,460 --> 00:04:48,500
I didn't say I'm going home.

79
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,380
I'm not going.

80
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:52,580
Oh, you're not?

81
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,500
The red bean cakes miss you.

82
00:04:54,620 --> 00:04:56,460
The swing in the yard misses you, too.

83
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:57,940
But most importantly,

84
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,820
I miss you.

85
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:04,980
Ha, you miss me?

86
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,290
I guess you've missed the moment

87
00:05:06,290 --> 00:05:07,540
when you held Guyu and caressed her shoulders.

88
00:05:10,260 --> 00:05:11,300
You're so busy.

89
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:13,380
How could you spare some time to miss me?

90
00:05:13,820 --> 00:05:15,620
I can take care of myself.

91
00:05:17,060 --> 00:05:18,140
That won't do.

92
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:19,540
You can't take care of yourself

93
00:05:19,540 --> 00:05:20,900
the same as I do.

94
00:05:20,900 --> 00:05:21,820
I wouldn't be at ease.

95
00:05:24,540 --> 00:05:26,060
My goodness,

96
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:28,220
I've really underestimated you.

97
00:05:28,620 --> 00:05:30,500
